    "title": "关于修订《 京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1255758545874456576",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">尊敬的商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，针对</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1147722726895652864\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进行调整<span style=\"background: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年6月27日- 2025年7月3日，规则预计于2025年7月4日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">核心调整点：五星店铺认证范围调整为在京东开放平台入驻开店的旗舰店、专卖店、专营店、卖场店店铺。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; background: white; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">具体修订内容如下：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 19.85pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 19.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订模块</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt; border-image: initial;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt; border-image: initial;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: center; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; border-image: initial;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第五章第十八条 五星店铺认证规则</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.0%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">认证范围：在京东开放平台入驻开店的企业店铺。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.0%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">认证范围：在京东开放平台入驻开店的旗舰店、专卖店、专营店、卖场店店铺。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.0%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第五章 第二十一条 其他特殊要求</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.0%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">奶瓶奶嘴 支持认证店铺类型：旗舰店、专卖店、专营店、卖场店。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.0%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 15.75pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">删除。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
